          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " and in some areas understaffed after budget cuts, regular citizens have decided to take matters into their own hands. One increasingly popular tool used by these modern sleuths is social media groups, particularly on Facebook.",
