        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "By pooling information about cars which have been stolen and those found obviously abandoned, owners are sometimes able to reclaim their vehicle. Of course those rides are usually damaged, but it’s better than taking a total loss through an insurance claim.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
